A perfectly circular chamber serves as the nexus point for the binding sigil web that radiates from the archive-throne dais. @@mSilver channels@@N in the floor form a complex geometric pattern that connects to every sector of the catacomb's necromantic infrastructure. The nexus amplified and distributed the Matriarch's commands through the bound dead, creating a hierarchical control system that extended from the throne to every reclaimed laborer, every dreadguard sentry, and every sealed name in the registry. The east passage connects to the inner sanctum.
~
