Sepulcher Junction~
A junction beyond the inner sanctum chambers connects the Matriarch's domain to the descending passages that lead toward the exit levels. The @@mblood-memory inscriptions@@N on the walls begin to fade at this depth, their power attenuating as the passage moves away from the binding nexus above. The architecture transitions from the polished authority of the sepulcher to rougher, older stonework that predates even the original Nightfall chapel construction. The passage south leads toward the exit corridors, where the narrative of Nightfall reaches its unresolved conclusion.
