decree staff~
The staff served as the Last Auditor's instrument of final judgment: each name spoken while holding it was permanently recorded in the Nightfall master registry. The skull finial is carved from a single piece of bone and set with small amethysts in the eye sockets. Faint necromantic energy crackles along its length, and the iron is inscribed with a continuous spiral of legal formulas authorizing reclamation of the unclaimed dead.
~
