shard voice rootglass~
Pressing the shard to your ear, you hear a voice speaking in an old forest dialect. The words are fragmentary but recognizable: "...promised return. Promised the cairn would stand. They carved our names but changed the marks. The Third Bell rang and we could not leave. The roots remember what the stone forgot..." The voice loops endlessly, a spirit testimony captured in rootglass.
~
